<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>STA Russell Announcements</title><link>https://matthewspencesta.github.io/Daily-Announcements-RSS-Feed/rss.xml</link><description>Latest announcements from STA Russell</description><atom:link href="https://matthewspencesta.github.io/Daily-Announcements-RSS-Feed/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 11:53:39 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>Today is Wednesday, March 25th, 2026.</title><link>https://sta-russell.cdsbeo.on.ca/apps/pages/DailyAnnouncements</link><description>&lt;p&gt;It is a week 1 schedule.&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">6264c3fb82cc925be4c82129ab52dd914fcba593f0ae7eb06271e475d95d56fe</guid><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 07:53:39 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>A message from Mrs. Kwok:</title><link>https://sta-russell.cdsbeo.on.ca/apps/pages/DailyAnnouncements</link><description>&lt;p&gt;To live out the Lenten Works of Mercy, grade nine Religion students are running a clothing drive for St. Mary's Clothing Closet and other local charities. Please bring in any donations of clean, good condition clothes to room 127 before Easter.&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">df425d98a731719b79b9ac55dd6ef3f9b14d95d048de59ca42e9619781514ed5</guid><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 07:53:39 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>A message from Chaplaincy:</title><link>https://sta-russell.cdsbeo.on.ca/apps/pages/DailyAnnouncements</link><description>&lt;p&gt;if you're in grade 9-12 and would like to be a reader or participate behind the scenes at next week's Holy Thursday prayer service, please see Mr. Vonesch to sign up. We need lots of help for this one, so please go to the chapel to sign up today!&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">63f2349b313ea44a574a8f94eb9e4b10e3fb11e64a